These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, carrot, corn, zucchini
There are 4 different nationalities: american, mexican, pakistani, malaysian
1. the mexican is on the left of the american##1
2. the person eating lime is the malaysian##1
3. the pakistani is on the right of the american##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | zucchini | corn | carrot | lime   |
| Nationality   | mexican  | american     | pakistani   | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, hiking, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, handball, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | hiking | sudoku | magic-tricks | board-games    |
| Sport   | handball    | sailing      | basketball | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, baking, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, adventure, scientific, epic
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | woodworking | baking   | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | scientific | epic | adventure         |

