.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero, romance, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, rowing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | superhero | fantasy  | romance      |
| Sport         | handball | parkour   | rowing | golf |

