.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, cabbage, pumpkin
4 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, mouse, turtle
1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pumpkin | cabbage | papaya | grapefruit |
| Pet    | frog       | turtle | mouse | lizard     |

