.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indonesian, thai, french
4 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig, hedgehog, bird
1. the indonesian is on the far right##1
2. the french is on the left of the thai##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the thai##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | french | thai | colombian | indonesian |
| Pet           | goat      | hedgehog | bird | guinea-pig    |

