.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, funk, r&b, blues
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, frog, fish
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | funk | ambient | blues  |
| Pet           | frog | bird | fish       | hedgehog |

