.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, security-guard, social-worker, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, boat, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the person driving the subway is the mechanic##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer      | security-guard | mechanic |
| Transport   | motorbike          | scooter | boat     | subway    |

