2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | action       | horror | disaster   |
| Transport     | subway | skateboard | quad-bike   | taxi |

