3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | juice | tea  | water | 7up |
| Transport   | car | jet-ski | helicopter          | ship    |

