.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, tea, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, dubstep, soul
1. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | tea | coffee  | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | dubstep | soul           | funk   |

