3. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
