.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, chinese, british
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, subway, helicopter
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the british##1
3. the colombian is on the left of the chinese##1
4. the british is the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | chinese | egyptian | british   |
| Transport     | subway  | van    | airplane       | helicopter |

 